S.FORM: Emil Benko nalecuhan i Whiting, Indiana, nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput. 11 bulad 9 demiad, 1913 a mihca, Emil Benko, miunduay. (mapatay i 2007 a mihca) namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players
